ec4b49bb-66f9-444b-a6a9-a82266239768	The rate-sensitive two-year yield rose as much as three basis points to 4.24%, the highest since February 2025, while the benchmark 10-year yield added three basis points to 4.59%. Brent crude jumped 5% after the US and Iran exchanged fresh strikes, with the two sides offering conflicting statements on whether the Strait of Hormuz remains open.\r\n\r\nBefore it's here, it's on the Bloomberg Terminal\r\n\r\nLEARN MORE\r\n\r\nHomeBTV+Market DataOpinionAudioOriginalsMagazineEvents [...] Markets\r\n\r\n# Treasury Two-Year Yields Rise to Highest Since 2025 as Oil Jumps\r\n\r\nContact us:\r\n\r\nProvide news feedback or report an error\r\n\r\nConfidential tip?\r\n\r\nSend a tip to our reporters\r\n\r\nSite feedback:\r\n\r\nTake our Survey\r\n\r\nBy Matthew Burgess and Masaki Kondo\r\n\r\nUpdated on\r\n\r\n## Takeaways by Bloomberg AI\r\n\r\nTreasury two-year yields climbed to their highest level since early 2025 as renewed tensions in Iran pushed up oil prices, fanning speculation that the Federal Reserve will need to raise interest rates to combat inflation.	{"title": "Treasury Two-Year Yields Rise to Highest Since 2025 as Oil Jumps - Bloomberg.com", "format": "web", "source": "https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-13/treasury-two-year-yield-rises-to-highest-since-2025-on-oil-gain", "fetch_time": "1784029802410", "source_url": "https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-07-13/treasury-two-year-yield-rises-to-highest-since-2025-on-oil-gain", "chunk_index": 0, "source_type": "web", "total_chunks": 1, "published_date": "Mon, 13 Jul 2026 09:58:37 GMT", "parent_document_id": "6249ad45-d464-498f-9500-5f9e573ca23a"}	[-0.055323813,0.01300678,-0.050208256,0.013717274,-0.032929037,-0.0001093865,-0.024099963,0.08700238,0.015877176,0.01903177,-0.017648676,0.00942589,-0.064114995,0.0014967744,-0.03997714,-0.040052924,0.10503946,0.040280282,-0.037305683,-0.030541778,-0.05839315,0.06441814,-0.049298823,0.020405393,-0.017430792,0.05058718